oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Photograph of Sgt. Horace E. Collins
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A photograph of three soldiers with the flag of the United States in the background. Collins is seated in the center. All are without headgear and are wearing long sleeved shirts with dark neckties. Sgt. Horace E. Collins served in Co. E, 105th Supply Train, 55th Depot Brigade. Collins was from St. Elmo in Hamilton County, Tennessee.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Collins, Horace E.
